    "content": "Janabe Umme Salma was widowed in medina & in difficulty when she requested the Prophet (pbuh) for a dua. The prophet asked her to recite this Dua.\r\n\r\nAs a consequence she became the wife of the Best human being on earth!, when there was NO hope of earning respect & a decent living.\r\n\r\n--بِسْمِ اللهِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ اِنَّا لِلّٰهِ وَ اِنَّا اِلَیْهِ رَاجِعُوْنَ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ اجْعَلْنِیْ فَرَجًا وَّ مَخْرَجًا وَّ ارْزُقْنِیْ خَیْرَ مِنْ حَیْثُ اَحْتَسِبُ وَ مِنْ حَیْثُ لَآ اَحْتَسِبُ بِحَقِّ مُحَمَّدٍ وَّ اٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ۔", 
    "audio": "", 
    "transliteration": "BISMILLAHIR RAHMANIR RAHEEM INNA LILLAHI WA INNA ILAIHI RAJE OON ALLAHUMMAJALNI FARAJAN WA MAKHRAJAN WAR ZUQNI KHAYRA MIN HAISO AHTASIBO WA MIN HAISO LA AHTASIB, BE HAQQE MOHAMMADIN WA ALE MOHAMMAD", 
    "english": "..Let my affairs be free from care & make them profitable & give me means of livelihood from my share & from where I have no expectation.."
}